title: Controversial calls in Packers-Lions, Ranking NFC's Top 5 Teams (Football 10/15)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap the Packers MNF victory over the Lions with a heavy emphasis on the questionable officiating that took place (2:30). The guys issue more of a game breakdown (25:00), what's next for each team and if the Packers could still be frauds at 5-1. Next up, the SuperFriends rank the NFC's Top 5 teams (41:00).
